A RESOLUTION
1 Recognizing and commending Boy With a Ball; and for other purposes.
2 WHEREAS, Boy With a Ball was founded in 2001 by Executive Director Jamie Johnson in
3 San Antonio, Texas, with the mission of developing young people and implementing scalable
4 solutions to address community needs; and
5 WHEREAS, since its inception, Boy With a Ball has launched over 50,000 youth as
6 changemakers, inspiring citywide movements to revitalize struggling neighborhoods in
7 Atlanta, across the United States, and in Latin America, Africa, and the Middle East; and
8 WHEREAS, the organization has further dedicated 435,380 volunteer hours, engaged 9,786
9 volunteers, facilitated 723 small groups, and fostered 3,034 mentoring relationships; and
10 WHEREAS, in a groundbreaking achievement, Boy With a Ball played a central role in
11 developing the El Triangulo de la Solidaridad squatter's settlement in San Jos√©, Costa Rica,
12 through its Love Your City initiative in partnership with the United States; and
13 WHEREAS, in recognition of its outstanding contributions to social progress, Boy With a
14 Ball was granted special consultative status with the United Nations Economic and Social
